{"tid":995482,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【時光機】趙國雄：嵐山非劏盤 「177呎唔係好細」","createTime":"2019-01-25T12:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T12:56:57.000Z","uid":19552,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e19da73244253f1086dcc4a2c02e71c2c1e4e6f8","tid":995482,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"長實（001）新盤大埔嵐山1期，自上周推出價單以及屋苑內有巨墳，長實執行董事趙國雄今早到電台解畫，否認為「賺到盡」推出超細單位。他表示：項目每平方呎售價只是7000元至8000元，貼近現時興建新樓盤的「成本價」，「唔係賺到盡，係平，單價（呎價）又平，總價都平。」他指出，賣2萬元一呎，才算是「賺到盡」。<br />\n<br />\n對於樓盤出現最細177呎單位，他否認是「劏房」格局，「我哋最細嘅單位177呎都唔係好細，如果劏房有咁大，咁住緊劏房嘅市民會好高興。」趙國雄指出，「已經是四五年前入則，無考慮到（今日）劏房流行。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20140721/large/1405931489_a464.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20140721%2Flarge%2F1405931489_a464.jpg&h=4df8563c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba4e05b12680dc42771df3fa7a9f4ef36a0dfe58","tid":995482,"uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:38:24.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀<br />\n<br />\n趙國雄：「200呎不適合人居住」 續料納米樓跌三成<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/995159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/995159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dd790a8bb60d3ce2d1b983e28e69b683ab8253fe","tid":995482,"uid":46835,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"真係小心俾天收呀講d咁嘅嘢....<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4807bff9a3fda746b1c006b6cc08ca021c62b311","tid":995482,"uid":13644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:44:47.000Z","msg":"即刻俾人抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee2c3bff6a5be00ce0ac9b8a11cd302ff06313f","tid":995482,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T13:26:20.000Z","msg":"但劏得最盡係四叔"},{"pid":"8b4a293f94335a1e1d5eefdf61d4e3e29820cdbb","tid":995482,"uid":201583,